OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, For the first time, journalists will be
OL,6, able to report what happens in family  
OL,7, courts, under a pilot scheme.          
OL,9,FUntil now, reporters have been able to 
OL,10,Fobserve hearings but could only report 
OL,11,Fwhat was allowed by a judge.           
OL,13,FThe 12-month pilot, which will not     
OL,14,Fallow journalists to identify families,
OL,15,Ftakes place in Leeds, Cardiff and      
OL,16,FCarlisle from the end of January.      
OL,18,FFamily courts have powers to make      
OL,19,Fdrastic interventions - such as        
OL,20,Fordering children be taken into care.  
